  "rationale": "One statement-beat hero only, adapting the hero-mission-monument archetype: a dead-centered mission monument on the brand's sanctioned opening dark band (surfaceIntent inverse), the ONE section allowed to carry the accent \u2014 placed on the display-title's closing period. The oversized serif statement leads, a single conviction line advances it with new specifics (empathy at scale, customer-aligned success), and restraint holds: just one quiet 'Read our story' link, no conversion furniture. A framed, subordinate workplace photograph sits BELOW the type as the altarpiece base \u2014 media never carries text, honoring no-text-on-photos. Centered anchor keeps the framed media symmetric (no misregistration). Heading stays sentence case at weight-500 tier per never-heavy-headings; no mid-page dark band beyond this opening bookend."
